This is a guide that should help you on your way to becoming a game developer, no matter what which path you want to take. This book should either help you through each aspect, or redirect you to a place that can. This book has been designed to be 'straight' and 'to the point' to allow you to make the most of your time. If you have found a section of the book that's lacking and you feel like you know enough to write about it, feel free to edit it, it will also help you get a better understanding of the topic.
__NOTOC__ __NOEDITSECTION__ == Categories == * {{stage short|25%}} <big>'''[[/Introduction/]]'''</big> ::: An introduction about me, the book and how it can help you. * {{stage short|25%}} <big>'''[[/Theory/]]'''</big> ::: The theory, logic, mathematics and understand behind how a game works. * {{stage short|0%}} <big>'''[[/Platform/]]'''</big> ::: The platform that the game is going to be developed for. * {{stage short|25%}} <big>'''[[/Rendering and Game Engines/]]'''</big> ::: The tool/framework/engine that you're going to use to create the game. * {{stage short|25%}} <big>'''[[/The Programming Language/]]'''</big> ::: The programming languages that are going to be used to create the games. * {{stage short|0%}} <big>'''[[/Data file types/]]'''</big> ::: The data file types used for storing information about the game. * {{stage short|0%}} <big>'''[[/Graphics and textures/]]'''</big> ::: The creation of effective appealing graphics and textures for games. * {{stage short|0%}} <big>'''[[/3D Modelling/]]'''</big> ::: The creation of 3D models used for characters, terrain and more! * {{stage short|0%}} <big>'''[[/Audio/]]'''</big> ::: The music and sound effects that will accompany the game. * {{stage short|0%}} <big>'''[[/Online Connectivity and Multiplayer/]]'''</big> ::: Connecting your game to the internet and to other players * {{stage short|75%}} <big>'''[[/Settings/]]'''</big> ::: All the items that could be added into a game settings menu. * {{stage short|0%}} <big>'''[[/Legal and Publishing/]]'''</big> ::: The legal and publishing side of game development. * {{stage short|25%}} <big>'''[[/Miscellaneous/]]'''</big> ::: All other subjects related to game development.
