{{Simple Page Navigation|BookName=[[Source SDK: Mastering the Source]]|CurrentPage=NPCs|PrevPage=[[Source SDK: Mastering the Source/Creating a Prefab|Creating a Prefab]]|NextPage=[[Source SDK: Mastering the Source/Making the Land|Making the Land]]}}
NPCs, or Non Player Characters are computer controlled characters in video games. In this case, they are placed throughout your map via entity place marker. Half-Life 2 features a variety of NPCs, both friendly and hostile.
